metadata.name: Bruises
metadata.description:
We get bruised and injured often in our rigorous fun adventures, and while we end up with bruises and scars, we learn and grow stronger along the way.

This illustration is part of my "Naked Thoughts" collection, which explores our most vulnerable state and the feelings that come with it.⁣⁣



4724 px x 5906 px
300 DPI
1/1  mixed media illustration
